  </div>
</section>

<!-- ====== FAQ ====== -->
<section class="th-faq">
  <div class="th-faq__container">
    <h2 class="th-faq__heading fade-in">Common questions</h2>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">What conditions can I get diagnosed for?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">Our providers specialize in Malassezia-related skin conditions: fungal acne (Malassezia folliculitis), seborrheic dermatitis, and tinea versicolor. All three are caused by the same yeast overgrowth and require specific treatment approaches.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">How does the consultation work?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">You'll have a consultation with a licensed provider (MD, DO, or NP). Before your visit, you'll fill out an intake form and upload photos of your skin. Your provider will review your history, examine your photos, and provide a diagnosis and treatment plan.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Can I get a prescription?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">Yes. If your provider determines you need prescription treatment, they can send e-prescriptions directly to your preferred pharmacy, including antifungals and other medications commonly used for Malassezia-related conditions.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Is this covered by insurance?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">Coverage varies by insurance plan. Many plans cover virtual dermatology visits. We recommend checking with your insurance provider before booking. We'll provide you with the information needed to submit a claim.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">How is my health information protected?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">All consultations are conducted through a HIPAA-compliant platform. Your medical information is encrypted, securely stored, and never shared with third parties. The care platform is separate from our e-commerce site to ensure full compliance.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">I already used the Ingredient Checker. Should I still book?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">The Ingredient Checker helps you identify products that may be feeding Malassezia, but it can't diagnose your condition. A licensed provider can confirm whether you're dealing with fungal acne, seb derm, or tinea versicolor and prescribe targeted treatment that over-the-counter products can't provide.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">How much does a consultation cost?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a" data-price="faq_pricing">Treatment Plans are $59.99/month, $69.99 every 2 months, or $149 quarterly — all include your provider consultation and prescription sent to your pharmacy. A one-time consult is available for $79. Optional delivery + medication add-on is $50/month. Payment is processed securely through Stripe.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">Do I need to upload photos of my skin?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">Photos are optional but highly recommended. You can upload up to 5 photos during the booking process. All GPS and device metadata is automatically stripped for your privacy, and photos are only visible to your treating provider.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">How do I select a pharmacy?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">During the booking process, you'll search for pharmacies by name and ZIP code. If your provider prescribes medication, the e-prescription will be sent directly to the pharmacy you selected.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="th-faq__item fade-in">
      <button class="th-faq__q" type="button">What payment methods do you accept?</button>
      <div class="th-faq__a">We accept all major credit and debit cards through Stripe, including Visa, Mastercard, American Express, and Discover. Apple Pay and Google Pay are also supported.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.th-faq__q').forEach(function(btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
      var answer = this.nextElementSibling;
      var isOpen = answer.classList.contains('open');
      document.querySelectorAll('.th-faq__a').forEach(function(a) { a.classList.remove('open'); });
      document.querySelectorAll('.th-faq__q').forEach(function(q) { q.classList.remove('active'); });
      if (!isOpen) {
        answer.classList.add('open');
        this.classList.add('active');
      }
    });
  });

  // Dynamic pricing from Supabase — single source of truth
  (function() {
    var SUPABASE_URL = 'https://pbriwsgraemyqhkymneq.supabase.co';
    var SUPABASE_KEY = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6InBicml3c2dyYWVteXFoa3ltbmVxIiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUwNTQxNjEsImV4cCI6MjA5MDYzMDE2MX0.AFfCsWNblX3MzjOJVRL7JefLzaLQrsc6xHSeDZuFWrI';

    fetch(SUPABASE_URL + '/rest/v1/pricing_config?select=key,value', {
      headers: { 'apikey': SUPABASE_KEY }
    })
    .then(function(r) { return r.json(); })
    .then(function(prices) {
      var p = {};
      // Preserve decimals — don't round $59.99 to $60
      prices.forEach(function(row) {
        var n = Number(row.value);
        // Strip trailing .00 but keep decimals like .99
        p[row.key] = (n % 1 === 0) ? String(Math.round(n)) : n.toFixed(2).replace(/\.?0+$/, '');
      });

      // Update plan card prices (uses CSS class for suffix styling)
      var monthlyEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_monthly"]');
      if (monthlyEl && p.treatment_monthly) {
        monthlyEl.innerHTML = '$' + p.treatment_monthly + '<span class="th-plan__price-suffix">/mo</span>';
      }
      var bimonthlyEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_bimonthly"]');
      if (bimonthlyEl && p.treatment_bimonthly) {
        bimonthlyEl.innerHTML = '$' + p.treatment_bimonthly + '<span class="th-plan__price-suffix">/2mo</span>';
      }
      var qtrEl = document.querySelector('[data-price="treatment_quarterly"]');
      if (qtrEl && p.treatment_quarterly) {
